# AutoCon FYP — Security Hardening & Feature Completion

Complete the AutoCon Web3 token deployment platform by fixing three critical security vulnerabilities (rate limiting, authentication, CORS), then adding the remaining FYP features: MetaMask Web3 login, gas estimator, and smart contract security audit.

