## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests (curl commands to run against the backend)

After starting the server with `cd d:\Autocon-fyp\server && node index.js`:

1. **CORS test** — Verify that requests from unauthorized origins are blocked:
   ```
   curl -H "Origin: http://evil.com" -v http://localhost:5000/api/health
   ```
   Expected: No `Access-Control-Allow-Origin` header or value not matching `http://evil.com`

2. **Rate limit test** — Hit the health endpoint rapidly:
   ```
   for /L %i in (1,1,105) do @curl -s -o nul -w "%{http_code}\n" http://localhost:5000/api/health
   ```
   Expected: After 100 requests, starts returning `429`

3. **Auth test** — Try accessing a protected route without JWT:
   ```
   curl -v http://localhost:5000/api/my-tokens/0x123
   ```
   Expected: `401 Unauthorized`

4. **Auth flow test** — Get nonce, (manual MetaMask signing can't be automated), verify JWT:
   ```
   curl http://localhost:5000/api/auth/nonce/0xYourWallet
   ```
   Expected: Returns `{ nonce: "..." }`

